data.title: Expensive and inexperienced
data.text: I have been to several massage places over the years and I found this Massage Envy to be waaaaay too expensive for the services I received from what was clearly an new, inexperienced MT. $95/hr non-member rate is ridiculous.

data.title: Non-transparent business practises
data.text: Although massages are OK, Massage Envy has very murky business practices. The membership is supposed to provide a member with a 1-hour massage each month, however all massages I had were less then 50 minutes. It is also very cumbersome to cancel membership.
